sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / CI Pipeline
    participant CLI as odh-cli<br/>(rhai-cli / kubectl-odh)
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OLM as OLM<br/>(Subscriptions / CSVs)
    participant GitHub as GitHub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over User,K8s: Flow 1: Lint / Upgrade Readiness Assessment
        User->>CLI: rhai-cli lint --target-version=3.0
        CLI->>K8s: GET DSC/DSCI CRDs<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: DSC/DSCI resources
        CLI->>K8s: GET OLM Subscriptions/CSVs<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Operator versions & status
        CLI->>K8s: LIST Notebooks, InferenceServices,<br/>RayClusters, PyTorchJobs, AppWrappers<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Workload resources
        Note over CLI: Execute 37 checks across<br/>5 groups (Dep→Svc→Platform→<br/>Component→Workload)
        CLI-->>User: DiagnosticResults<br/>(table/JSON/YAML)<br/>Exit code 0-5
    end

    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
        Note over User,OLM: Flow 2: Dependency Installation
        User->>CLI: rhai-cli deps install
        CLI->>K8s: LIST OLM Subscriptions<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Existing subscriptions
        Note over CLI: Compare against<br/>odh-gitops manifest
        CLI->>K8s: CREATE Namespace<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Namespace created
        CLI->>K8s: CREATE OperatorGroup<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: OperatorGroup created
        CLI->>K8s: CREATE OLM Subscription<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Subscription created
        loop Poll for completion
            CLI->>K8s: GET ClusterServiceVersion<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
            K8s-->>CLI: CSV status (Pending/Installing/Succeeded)
        end
        CLI-->>User: Installation result
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over User,K8s: Flow 3: Kueue RHBOK Migration
        User->>CLI: rhai-cli migrate prepare kueue-rhbok
        CLI->>K8s: GET DSC (check Kueue state)<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: DSC with Kueue Managed
        CLI->>K8s: GET ClusterQueues, ConfigMaps<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Resources (backup)
        CLI->>K8s: PATCH ConfigMap<br/>annotate managed=false<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: ConfigMap patched
        User->>CLI: rhai-cli migrate run kueue-rhbok
        CLI->>K8s: CREATE RHBOK Subscription<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Subscription created
        CLI->>K8s: PATCH DSC (Kueue→Unmanaged)<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
        Note over CLI: Exponential backoff<br/>with jitter for<br/>conflict resolution
        K8s-->>CLI: DSC patched
        CLI-->>User: Migration complete
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over CLI,GitHub: Flow 4: Dependency Manifest Refresh
        User->>CLI: rhai-cli deps check --refresh
        CLI->>GitHub: GET values.yaml, Chart.yaml<br/>from odh-gitops repo<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: None (public)
        GitHub-->>CLI: Updated manifest files
        Note over CLI: Parse Helm charts<br/>for operator dependencies
        CLI->>K8s: LIST OLM Subscriptions/CSVs<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Current operator state
        CLI-->>User: Dependency status report
    end
